{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "深夜，韦好客冒着严寒闯入慕容秋水寝室，只说了三个字\"班沙克\"。丁丁（丁宁）被关在牢房中已百余天，他用汤匙碎片在墙上刻下\"班沙克\"三字，确信韦好客看到后会来找慕容秋水。慕容秋水与韦好客深夜密谈，回忆\"班沙克\"的由来——当年四个少年花错、韦好客、慕容秋水和丁宁潜入王府后园，与异域美女葛蕾丝寻欢作乐，葛蕾丝用家乡话称他们为\"班沙克\"（大鲨鱼），从此成为四人间的秘密暗号。二人确认牢中贵宾就是丁宁，而因梦故意将丁宁弄瞎弄哑、改换面容后送来此处，意在报复。二人商议后决定不能放丁宁出来，因为错已铸成，只能错到底。韦好客提议借官方刽子手之手除掉丁宁以绝后患，慕容秋水默认但要求撇清关系。韦好客离去后，慕容秋水差点杀死身旁侍妾伴伴灭口，但伴伴浑然不觉地翻身撒娇，令他打消了杀意。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "韦先生，韦大老爷，你既然来了，为什么不干脆推门走进来？难道你还想要我起来为你开门？难道你想活活的把我冻死？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我知道你没有喝醉，因为你从来都不喝酒的，你看起来也不像是发了疯的样子，所以我实在觉得很奇怪，你为什么会在这种时候闯到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我希望你有一个很好的解释，否则我不剥了你的皮、把你赤条条的扔到阴沟里去才怪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "班沙克。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "班沙克。我的确有好久没有听到这三个字了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "可是你三更半夜的闯到我这里来，总不会只为了要告诉我这三个字吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我还要问你，你还记不记得这三个字是什么意思？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我怎么会忘记？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "就算等到我老掉牙的时候，我也不会忘记那天晚上……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你当然也应该知道，这个世界上现在还有多少人明白这三个字的意思。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "本来有五个人的，后来变成了四个，现在恐怕只剩下三个了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "事隔多年，你为什么忽然又提起这三个字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "因为我今天又看见这三个字了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "在什么地方看到的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "就在我最特别的那间雅座的墙上，而且是你请来的那位贵宾用牙咬着一个汤匙的碎片画上去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "他怎么会知道这三个字的？难道因梦娘送来的那位贵宾就是……？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "班沙克，你们这些小鬼简直是一群班沙克。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尤其是你，你是一个超级的大班沙克。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "瘦小男孩",
      "listener": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "text": "为什么我是超级的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你只会咬人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了咬人之外，你什么都不会。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "男孩",
      "listener": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "text": "班沙克是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在我们那里的语言中，'班'的意思就是大，'沙克'的意思就是一种鱼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一种会吃人的鱼，也就是你们说的鲨鱼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种鱼在吃人的时候，总会咧开它的大嘴，看起来就好像是在笑一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_lei_si",
      "speaker_name": "葛蕾丝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种大鲨鱼，要吃人的时候，简直就跟你们现在这个样子差不多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "丁宁、花错、因梦，这三个人之间究竟在搞什么鬼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "不管怎么样，那条母狗这次可真是让我上了贼船，她明明知道我们跟丁宁是从小在一起长大的死党，为什么还要把他送到这里来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "她当然是故意的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "所以她才会让丁宁看不见也说不出，甚至把他的脸都动过了，让我们也认不出他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "她知道我们跟丁宁是朋友，当然是从花错那里听来的，她不但恨丁宁，也恨我，所以才想出这种法子来整我们两个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我可以想得出她为什么会恨我，可是我实在想不出丁宁为什么要杀花错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "如果你一定要问理由，恐怕只有去问丁宁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "对，我们去问丁宁。我们已经把他整惨了，不管怎么样，现在都要把他先弄出来再说。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "不行。我们绝不能放他出来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "因为我们从一开始就错了，而且错得很多，所以我们只有错到底。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "要怎么样做，才算错到底？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "丁宁不死，后患无穷，如果你以后还想能够安安心心的睡觉，他就非死不可，而且死得愈快愈好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我当然不会要你去杀他，我也不会去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "如果我们杀了他，以后就永远有个把柄被你那位因梦夫人捏在手里，那我们以后恐怕更没有好日子过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "她能抓住我们什么把柄。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "如果丁将军知道他的儿子是死在我们手里的，我们还会不会有一天好日子过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "只有一种人杀人是完全不用负责任的，也不会有后患。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "他们杀人根本是天经地义的事，谁也不会找他们报仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你说的是哪种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "刽子手。有资格的刽子手，而且是被官方承认的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "刑部大牢里，有一名犯人，犯了杀头的重罪，被一个官方的刽子手处决，这种事是谁也不能过问的，所以永无后患。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "这一类的事，我相信你一定可以安排的很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "大概可以。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "可是你一定要记住，这件事跟我连一点关系都没有，刚刚说的话我也连一个字都没有听见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我相信你一定也明白，我刚刚说的那些话，无论谁只要听见了一个字，那个人就非死不可。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你的手好冷。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "刚才你一定没有把你的手放在我这里，我这里好热好热。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "刚才我一定是睡着了，否则我一定不会让你的手放在被窝外面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_ban_ban",
